  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test the hypothesis that obstructive sleep apnea syndrome is
      associated with deviant pharyngeal swallowing function, using clinical, endoscopical and
      manometric evaluation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
